{"tid":2367332,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"吳奇隆新股升90%爆冷跑出！持股稻草熊值8億 每手最多賺5,480元多過醫渡","createTime":"2021-01-15T09:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T16:14:31.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab4ac75b9514ac8a1a8d86fcc210052360518595","tid":2367332,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T09:03:23.000Z","msg":"劉詩詩持有稻草熊11%股權<br />\n稻草熊由吳奇隆創辦，為中國劇集製片商及發行商，目前由其妻子劉詩詩持有11.1%股權。該股今日最高見11.36元，市值最高見75.3億元，吳奇隆夫婦持股價值曾達到8.36億元。<br />\n<br />\n招股反應較遜色的榮萬家（2146）屬唯一破發股，最新報12.36元，較招股價低8%；現代中藥（1643）較招股價高6.8%，報1.26元。<br />\n<br />\n信誠證券聯席董事張智威表示，五隻新股中最看好醫渡科技，皆因科技股、雲業務為熱炒版塊，升1.5倍非正常，惟現時估值過高，認為投資者不應心急追貨，可在55元以下作吸納，短線企穩60元，值得中長線持有；其餘股份如稻草熊及網上車市，他認為炒作成分高，不宜高追。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210115/3VXRDTZOIFGOTPUJPKKWFP366E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210115%2F3VXRDTZOIFGOTPUJPKKWFP366E%2F&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=c5e91fc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210115%2F3VXRDTZOIFGOTPUJPKKWFP366E%2F&h=471d0f1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210115/3VXRDTZOIFGOTPUJPKKWFP366E/</a>"},{"pid":"f6802b552cb72900ecd96f39170fff124150677c","tid":2367332,"uid":286928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:53:57.000Z","msg":"恭喜上市/暗盤  開市入既賭仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad94b96b7bac8f88520ed0f65f13a5aaed2c859","tid":2367332,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:08:49.000Z","msg":"琴日暗盤好多人俾佢呃左隻熊。<br />\n<br />\n可惜冇抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63903bec21f453048c9e15d11d6b36fd05ea6f36","tid":2367332,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T11:22:35.000Z","msg":"蔡少芬有冇買"},{"pid":"84171ac51f8476015922fb56930705d3cfc9ac8b","ti